<plot>In a North German Boarding School for Boys, one Pupil, Kurrat, suddenly vanishes one night without informing anybody. Soon, the Police under the aegis of Inspector Klevenow has to learn that Kurrat was a very mysterious, intelligent but also rude person, adored by his roommates, desired by the girls, hated by most of the teachers but obviously passionately loved by one of them. The Investigation reveals dozens of different possible motives for murder - Has somebody been jealous, vengeful, disappointed or betrayed? Has someone killed Kurrat and plunged his body into the near sea? When Stallmann, the teacher with whom Kurrat is said to have had a love affair, and Kurrats father are found dead, the mystery grows. When Kurrat finally and unexpectedly reappears, things get even more enigmatic.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?496243</url></doc>
